headline: NextEra Energy: Valuation Compression Is A Slow Motion Train Wreck
summary: We had suggested that investors choose Pinnacle West over NextEra Energy. We now review how that trade performed. Read our review of the Q4-2024 results for NextEra and our updated outlook.
